snippet.title: Rush E Impossible Piano Duet (4 hands plus elbow!)
snippet.description:
*SCORE AVAILABLE FOR PURCHASE! https://www.musicnotes.com/l/7khMQ 

Check out our new Rush 🅱️ + Flight of the Bumblebee Mash Up! https://youtu.be/JN8PHaF1LZs

https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=qbEBrMZ-G_k Check out our 8-hands version of Rush E, with the original legends themselves, Fanchen and ProLitening! 

Our student Fanchen from the other side of the country gave us a call a week ago and told us about the “Rush E” drama that he was part of - this inspired us to take the challenge of arranging and performing the “humanly impossible” original Sheet Music Boss MIDI version for piano 4 hands/piano duet!

So, is this performance mediocre, Fanchen?

Original music by Andrew Wrangell
Piano 4 hands arrangement by The Meeks Duo

Fanchen’s performance: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=on4IoQ2MQ7M
Sheet Music Boss Original: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Qskm9MTz2V4
Youtuber Charlie's Cr1TiKaL explaining the drama: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=foSAi-olfck

Scott Meek, primo
